        {
          "text": "Finally, on [WebArena⁠(opens in a new window)](https://webarena.dev/), a benchmark designed to evaluate the performance of web-browsing agents in completing real-world web tasks, the model improves over o3‑powered CUA (the model powering Operator).",
          "charCount": 248
